@startuml ambient_mode_to_ivi_render_signal_flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title Ambient Mode To IVI Render Signal Flow\n(BCM ambient ownership -> IVI render seams -> cabin animation)

participant "Cmd / alert context" as AmbientCtx #F4F7FB
participant "BCM\nambient owner" as BCM #E8F7E8
participant "IVI\nrender owner" as IVI #FFF4CC
participant "UiRender / panels" as RenderObs #E8F0FE

== Ambient Ownership ==

AmbientCtx -> BCM : Cmd::ambientModeCmd\nalertLevel / alertType / timeoutClear
BCM -> BCM : derive AmbientMode / AmbientColor / AmbientPattern
BCM -> BCM : publish Body::ambientMode / Color / Pattern
note right of BCM
Representative ownership outputs
- Body::ambientMode
- Body::ambientColor
- Body::ambientPattern
end note

== Render Translation ==

BCM -> IVI : Body::ambientMode / Color / Pattern
IVI -> IVI : renderMode = Body::ambientMode
IVI -> IVI : renderColor = Body::ambientColor
IVI -> IVI : renderPattern = Body::ambientPattern
IVI -> IVI : cabinAmbientAnimFrame = deriveCabinAmbientAnimFrame(...)
IVI -> RenderObs : UiRender::renderMode / renderColor / renderPattern
IVI -> RenderObs : UiRender::ambientPulsePhase / cabin ambient animation
note right of IVI
Representative render outputs
- UiRender::renderMode
- UiRender::renderColor
- UiRender::renderPattern
- cabin ambient animation frame
end note

note over AmbientCtx, RenderObs
Representative runtime chain
1. Ambient mode is owned in BCM from manual or alert context
2. BCM publishes stabilized body ambient state
3. IVI translates ambient state into render seams and animation frames
4. Panels consume UiRender seams as visible cabin ambient output
end note

@enduml
